      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王氏上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00002",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "小调转五更",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "怕到黄昏，怕到黄昏，黄昏已定，起了初更。忙开梳妆匣，架起了青铜镜，手挽乌云，手挽乌云。漫天星斗照乾坤，忽听得，撞罢钟，就把更来定，撞罢钟，就把更来定。",
      "text_length": 75
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00003",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "人生最苦是别离，难舍难分没了期。相逢相见知何日，死别生离两处飞。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00004",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "奴家王氏。丈夫花大汉，在营中吃了一分口粮，明日大老爷要起兵出征，我丈夫要从征出战。为此奴家，备了些酒肴在此，与他饯行。怎么这般时候，还不见回来？",
      "text_length": 72
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00005",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "花大汉上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00006",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花大汉"
      ],
      "text": "咳。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00007",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "花大汉"
      ],
      "text": "为人莫当兵，做铁莫做钉。做钉被人打，当兵受苦情。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00008",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花大汉"
      ],
      "text": "我，花大汉的便是。今早在辕门伺候，大老爷发令起兵，方才又传出令来，明早五鼓，就要起程。我想此番前去，不知胜败如何，生死难料。只得回来，与妻子分别一番。来此已是自己家门了。老婆开门来。",
      "text_length": 91
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00009",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "是谁呀？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00010",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花大汉"
      ],
      "text": "是我。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00011",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "当家的回来啦，待我开门。哟，你回来啦！",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00012",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花大汉"
      ],
      "text": "我回来了。咳，我当初为什么要当他娘的兵。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00013",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "我说当家的，大老爷几时起程呀？",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00014",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花大汉"
      ],
      "text": "大老爷明日就要起程了。我是实实舍不得你，故此回来，与你分别。我的腰刀兵器，铺盖行李，可曾打点好了靡有？",
      "text_length": 51
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00015",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "全给你预备好啦。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00016",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花大汉"
      ],
      "text": "你先拿我的铺盖来。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00017",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "做什么呀？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00018",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花大汉"
      ],
      "text": "我先睡一会，到了五更天，就要开腿上路了。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00019",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "奴家备得些酒肴在此，特与你饯饯行。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00020",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花大汉"
      ],
      "text": "有酒？好，拿来咱们喝。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00021",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "来了。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00022",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王氏送酒，斟。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00023",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "一更鼓儿天，一更那鼓儿天。我儿夫征西摆着酒筵，摆酒筵，就把行来饯。好伤怀，望丈夫早回归，早回归，与奴重相见。",
      "text_length": 54
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00024",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花大汉"
      ],
      "text": "干！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00025",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "打二更鼓。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00026",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "二更鼓儿深，二更那鼓儿深。你去不知，何日再相亲，你须记妻子，我身怀孕。",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00027",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花大汉"
      ],
      "text": "你有了喜了么？我好伤心吓，也没个人来扶侍你，好苦呀！",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00028",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "奴好伤心！奴好伤心！去到边关万里长城，到了时，早寄阳关信。到了时，早寄一封阳关信。",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00029",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花大汉"
      ],
      "text": "咳！边关上，恐怕靡有人可以带信与你。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00030",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "打三更鼓。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00031",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "三更鼓儿催，三更那鼓儿催，奴劝丈夫你多吃几杯！",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00032",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花大汉"
      ],
      "text": "待我多喝几杯。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00033",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "吃几杯，好与你同床睡。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00034",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花大汉"
      ],
      "text": "嗳！我的骚娘呀，有什么心情，还想那话儿吗？一会儿就要拔腿上路了。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00035",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "奴好凄惶！奴好凄惶！只有今宵，与你同床。你不眠，叫奴可如何样？",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00036",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "花大汉倚桌睡。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00037",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "当家的睡吓。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00038",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "花大汉拔腰刀看。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00039",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花大汉"
      ],
      "text": "贼在哪里？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00040",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "我说是睡觉，哪儿有贼呀！",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00041",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花大汉"
      ],
      "text": "睡觉吓。呵呀，我的娘。明日上阵，要跑马射箭的，还干这个事吗？",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00042",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "打四更鼓。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00043",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "四更鼓儿沉，四更那鼓儿沉，只有今宵一刻千金。出门人，不好多相问，你此去，不知在哪处儿困。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00044",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花大汉"
      ],
      "text": "哪有什么好所在，不过是帐房里头罢了。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00045",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "一路小心！一路小心！你去后又有谁来问。你去后，谁来把你问。",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00046",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "打五更鼓。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00047",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "五更鼓儿敲，五更那鼓儿敲，奴对丈夫哭号啕。你若是早回归，再得与你同欢笑，你且莫心焦，你且莫心焦。巴得的早回来，与你同欢笑。",
      "text_length": 61
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00048",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "鸡叫。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00049",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花大汉"
      ],
      "text": "呵呀！不好了，天色明了。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00050",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "花大汉"
      ],
      "text": "天色明了，天色已明了，打点行李，挂在马鞍桥。我的姣姣，我去后，你休被旁人笑，我去后，你莫被旁人笑。",
      "text_length": 49
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00051",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "老二上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00052",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "老二"
      ],
      "text": "旁人笑，旁人笑，大老爷已放了起身炮。我好笑。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00053",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老二"
      ],
      "text": "花大汉昨晚上回家，今日这时候还不见到，又得我来叫他。说着，说着，到了。老大，开门来。",
      "text_length": 42
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00054",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花大汉"
      ],
      "text": "哪个小屄养的，天将亮就来打门！",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00055",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老二"
      ],
      "text": "嗳，怎么就骂起来了。老大，是我。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00056",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花大汉"
      ],
      "text": "待我开门看，原来是老二吓，得罪，得罪，家里坐。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00057",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老二"
      ],
      "text": "这是谁呀？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00058",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花大汉"
      ],
      "text": "这是你嫂子。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00059",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老二"
      ],
      "text": "婊子？待我来嫖嫖。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00060",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花大汉"
      ],
      "text": "嗳！是你嫂子。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00061",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老二"
      ],
      "text": "是嫂子。来见个礼儿。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00062",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花大汉"
      ],
      "text": "不见罢了。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00063",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老二"
      ],
      "text": "嫂子我这儿有礼了。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00064",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "这是谁？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00065",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花大汉"
      ],
      "text": "是你的二兄弟。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00066",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老二"
      ],
      "text": "老大，大老爷放了起身炮。头队二队，都开跋了，快些走罢。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00067",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "叔叔，大老爷已经起身了吗？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00068",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老二"
      ],
      "text": "走了好一会了。老大，快走罢。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00069",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王氏"
      ],
      "text": "呵呀，丈夫吓，你要早去早回，路上要保重！",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00070",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 70,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花大汉"
      ],
      "text": "老婆呀。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00071",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 71,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "花大汉"
      ],
      "text": "呵呀我的姣姣，我的姣姣。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017007_e00072",
      "play_id": "01017007",
      "scene_id": "01017007_s01",
